  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read Program.cs:21-30 current UseAzureMonitor block.</step>
    <step order="2">Read CacheModule.cs 4-branch fail-fast pattern for reference shape.</step>
    <step order="3">Implement: `if (env != "Development" &amp;&amp; string.IsNullOrEmpty(connectionString)) throw new InvalidOperationException("APPLICATIONINSIGHTS_CONNECTION_STRING is required in non-Development environments. Set via App Service config or KV reference.");`. Development branch unchanged.</step>
    <step order="4">Add unit test in `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Startup/` or appropriate location verifying both branches (Production throws; Development passes through).</step>
    <step order="5">§F.3 empirical reproduction: run BFF locally with `ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT=Production` + unset conn string; verify it throws on startup.</step>
    <step order="6">Build clean.</step>
    <step order="7">Run unit tests including new ones.</step>
    <step order="8">Update TASK-INDEX 🔲 → ✅.</step>
    <step order="9">Step 9.5 quality gates: code-review + adr-check.</step>
